!! USED CMSSW_7_0_2 -> for make (altrimenti errore)

download TMVA "tar-ball" from https://sourceforge.net/projects/tmva/files/
~> tar -zxvf TMVA-v4.2.0.tgz
~> cd TMVA-v4.2.0
~/TMVA-v4.2.0> make
~/TMVA-v4.2.0> cd test
~/TMVA-v4.2.0/test> source setup.sh

